{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7ca66e3bd6","title":"日前我军应坚持休整与退需敌人前进的方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ad3054830","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"412ab7c07d","type":"paragraph","text":"日前我军应坚持休整与退需敌人前进的方针！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"1d4197015d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月16日）任、贺、关、刘，并致朱、张”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"8df00375ce","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、十四日电悉。二方面军进至单家集、硝河城线后即可开始休息整理。该地区比较丰富，待一方面军执行新任务时接替对南防御任务，亦当有休息机会。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"0b00716bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、我三个方面军自前应以休息整理蓄积锐气准备执行新的战略任务为基本方针，对故采退带其前进方针。判断在敌情地形等条件下可能达此自的。即使船渡不成，我亦应坚持此方针，方于尔后行动有更大利益。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"f930a3a70c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛周","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"8b97fb05a7","type":"paragraph","text":"十六日二十二时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"e4d6cc71eb","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和周恩来给红军第二方面军政治委员任弱时、总指挥贺龙、副政治委员关向应和红军总参谋长兼第二方面军红军大学校长刘伯承等的电报。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"},{"id":"79879bca11","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]朱，指朱德。张，指张国意，当时任红军总政治委员。[3]单家集、硝河城，均位于今宁夏西吉县东南。单家集，今作单民。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6"}],"page":{"id":"f53edd39df","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"7ca66e3bd6","start":232,"end":232}}}},"__N_SSG":true}